name: Supa Team 4
overview: Four teens are just trying to survive secondary school when an ex-spy recruits them for her superhero team. Their newest assignment? Saving the world.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: While Mr. Magedzee searches for a cleaner, greener power source, Supa Team 4 searches for the evil Chusi. Will they all find what they're looking for?

episodes.name: Team 4 in the Byu Byu
episodes.overview: When a freak tornado sweeps through the city, four brave girls run headfirst into danger — attracting the attention of a woman who needs their help.

episodes.name: Hanger Management
episodes.overview: To stop a swarm of metal-eating locusts from destroying the city's dam, Team 4 must first help Temwe learn to control — and harness — her anger.

episodes.name: The Zee
episodes.overview: From saving the mayor to scoring a winning goal, Zee's ego is out of control. Can Supa Team 4 remember how to work together before it's too late?

episodes.name: The Monde Challenge
episodes.overview: When a homesick Monde's nerves get the best of her at a majorettes performance, her new crew must figure out how to support their friend.

episodes.name: Smart Art
episodes.overview: Brilliant Komana has a brain for science, not art. So when she struggles in her drawing class, inspiration has to come from an unexpected place.

episodes.name: Missing Kid
episodes.overview: Mama K has a special training assignment for the team: taking care of Chomps for the day. Can Team 4 prove they can handle the extra responsibility?

episodes.name: Herstory
episodes.overview: Supa Team 4 suspects Mama K is hiding something from them. But after brewing up interrogation tactics, the girls might not be ready for the truth.

episodes.name: Brain Power (1)
episodes.overview: While Chusi acts on a new strategy to destroy the city's power sources, the girls get one step closer to unmasking the villain. Go, go, Supa Team 4!

episodes.name: Brain Power (2)
episodes.overview: To free themselves from the mines and to keep their identities secret, Team 4 will have to remember the skills Mama K taught them — and get creative.

episodes.name: Zee vs. Tee
episodes.overview: Zee has her hands full with the triplets, Temwe has trouble connecting with her parents... and each girl thinks she has it worse. Solution? Life swap!

episodes.name: Click Bait
episodes.overview: Temwe needs to score an invite to a classmate's birthday celebration to see her favorite pop star perform, but an unwanted guest crashes the party.

episodes.name: Majorette Problem
episodes.overview: Monde unseats the former captain of the majorettes before an important audition, but teamwork comes in handy when the two girls least expect it.

episodes.name: Sisters Before Misters
episodes.overview: When Mr. Magedzee stands Monde's sister up for a date, Team 4 spends the day tailing him to figure out if he's ghosting, flexing or hiding something.

episodes.name: A Zambinite to Remember
episodes.overview: Komana could land an internship that would launch her on a path to success if she signs enough people up for Mr. Magedzee's new power program.

episodes.name: The Perfect Storm (1)
episodes.overview: When people at the marketplace come down with a mysterious sickness, the team wonders if it could be a coincidence — or something more sinister.
